'''塞鯨'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Balaenoptera borealis}}''）為[[鬚鯨|鬚鯨]]的一種，又名'''北须鲸'''<ref name='id587'/>，為世界上第三大鬚鯨，僅次於[[藍鯨|藍鯨]]與[[長鬚鯨|長鬚鯨]]<ref name="mfr">{{cite journal | author = S.L. Perry | coauthors = D.P. DeMaster, and G.K. Silber | year = 1999 | title = Special Issue: The Great Whales:  History and Status of Six Species Listed as Endangered Under the U.S. Endangered Species Act of 1973 | journal = Marine Fisheries Review | volume = 61 | issue = 1 | url = http://spo.nwr.noaa.gov/mfr611/mfr611.htm | pages = 52–58 | access-date = 2011-04-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721055959/http://spo.nwr.noaa.gov/mfr611/mfr611.htm | archive-date = 2011-07-21 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。牠們分布在世界各地的海域，尤其是在遠離海岸的海洋深層<ref name="Gambell85a">{{cite book | author = Gambell, R. | year = 1985 | chapter = Sei Whale 'Balaenoptera borealis'' Lesson, 1828 | pages= 155–170 | title = Handbook of Marine Mammals, Vol. 3 | editors = S.H. Ridgway and R. Harrison (eds) | publisher = Academic Press | location = London }}</ref>。塞鯨傾向避開陽光與熱帶海域，每年夏季時從寒冷或兩極的海域遷移到溫帶海域，冬季則遷移到亞熱帶海域，雖然大部分區域的遷移路線尚未完全明朗<ref name="nmfs"/>。

塞鯨身長可以達到20公尺（66英尺），體重則可達到45[[公噸|公噸]]（50[[短噸|短噸]]）<ref name="nmfs">{{cite book | author = Reeves, R. | coauthors = G. Silber and M. Payne | title = Draft Recovery Plan for the Fin Whale ''Balaenoptera physalus'' and Sei Whale ''Balaenoptera borealis'' | publisher = National Marine Fisheries Service | location = Silver Spring, Maryland | url = http://www.cresli.org/cresli/pdf%20documents/finwhale.pdf | format = PDF | date = 1998年7月 | access-date = 2007-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204014/http://www.cresli.org/cresli/pdf%20documents/finwhale.pdf | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。估計每天需要900公斤的食物，主要是[[橈腳類|橈腳類]]動物與[[磷蝦|磷蝦]]，有時還包括其他的[[軟體動物|軟體動物]]<ref name="adw">{{cite web | author = Shefferly, N. | year = 1999 | title = Balaenoptera borealis | publisher = Animal Diversity Web | url = http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Balaenoptera_borealis.html | accessdate = 2006-11-04 | archive-date = 2014-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140821091617/http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Balaenoptera_borealis.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。塞鯨的速度也是鯨魚中最快的，在短距離上可以達到每小時50公里（31[[英里|英里]]或27[[節|節]]）的速度。<ref name="adw"/>「塞鯨」這個名稱是從[[挪威語|挪威語]]的「Pollock」（青鱈）而來的，[[青鱈|青鱈]]是種與塞鯨同時間出現在[[挪威|挪威]]海岸邊的魚類<ref name="acs">{{cite web|url=http://www.acsonline.org/factpack/SeiBrydesWhales.htm |title=Sei Whale & Bryde's Whale ''Balaenoptera borealis'' & ''Balaenoptera edeni'' |publisher=American Cetacean Society |accessdate=2006-11-08 |date=2004年3月 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060927212353/http://www.acsonline.org/factpack/SeiBrydesWhales.htm |archivedate=2006-09-27 }}</ref>。

在19[[世紀|世紀]]後期至20世紀後期之間的大規模商業獵捕中，估計共有超過238,000條塞鯨被獵捕<ref name="horwood87">{{cite book | author = Horwood, J. | year = 1987 | title = The sei whale: population biology, ecology, and management | publisher = Croom Helm Ltd. | location = Kent, England |id=ISBN 978-0-7099-4786-8}}</ref>，而現在塞鯨已成為國際保育動物<ref name="iucn"/>，雖然[[冰島|冰島]]與[[日本|日本]]仍然有具有爭議的研究計劃在獵捕塞鯨<ref name="wwf05">{{cite press release|publisher=WWF-International |title=Japanese Scientific Whaling: Irresponsible Science, Irresponsible Whaling |date=2005-06-01 |url=http://www.panda.org/about_wwf/what_we_do/species/publications/index.cfm?uNewsID=13793 |accessdate=2006-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060825094925/http://www.panda.org/about_wwf/what_we_do/species/publications/index.cfm?uNewsID=13793 |archivedate=2006-08-25 }}</ref>。2006年時估計全球約有54,000條塞鯨，數量大約只剩大規模捕鯨活動前的5分之1<ref name="acs"/>。

== 分類學與命名 ==
-{zh-hans:[[File:Rorqual_phylogenetic_tree_zh_hans.svg|thumb]]]];zh-hant:[[File:Rorqual_phylogenetic_tree_zh_hant.svg|thumb]]]]}-
塞鯨最早是由[[法國|法國]][[自然學家|自然學家]][[雷納-普里莫弗勒·拉森|雷納-普里莫弗勒·拉森]]（René-Primevère Lesson）在1828年所描述的，但是進一步的敘述則是由德裔的自然學家[[卡爾·魯道費|卡爾·魯道費]]（Karl Rudolphi）所完成的。所以塞鯨有時又稱為'''魯道費鯨'''、'''卢氏须鲸'''（Rudolphi's Rorqual）、'''波拉克鯨'''（Pollack Whale）、'''鱈鯨'''（Coalfish Whale）、'''沙丁魚鯨'''（Sardine Whale）與'''日本脊鰭鯨'''（Japan Finner）<ref name="whalesonnet">{{cite web | url=http://www.whales.org.au/discover/sei/seig.html | title=Sei Whales (''Balaenoptera borealis'') | publisher=Whales on the net | accessdate=2006-11-29 | archive-date=2021-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301012724/https://whales.org.au/discover/sei/seig.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

''Sei''這個字是從挪威語中的''seje''而來，那是一種[[鱈魚|鱈魚]]（青鱈），被當地的居民稱為波拉克（Pollock）。這是因為塞鯨與青鱈在相同的時間出現在[[挪威|挪威]]海岸邊，一起捕食[[浮游生物|浮游生物]]。塞鯨的種名''borealis''意義為北方。塞鯨在太平洋被稱為日本鯨（Japan Finner）。塞鯨則在日本被稱為沙丁魚鯨（[[日文|日文]]:{{lang|ja|イワシヒゲクジラ}}），因為塞鯨在太平洋被觀察到在捕食沙丁魚。<ref name="natlgeo1911">{{cite journal | url = http://www.edwardtbabinski.us/whales/shore_whaling_industry.html | journal = National Geographic Magazine | title = Shore Whaling: A World Industry | author = Andrews, R.C. | date = May 1911 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161028204800/http://www.edwardtbabinski.us/whales/shore_whaling_industry.html | archivedate = 2016-10-28 }}</ref>

塞鯨屬於[[鬚鯨科|鬚鯨科]]，這個科包括[[藍鯨|藍鯨]]、[[大翅鯨|大翅鯨]]、[[布氏鯨|布氏鯨]]、[[長鬚鯨|長鬚鯨]]與[[小鬚鯨|小鬚鯨]]。鬚鯨在挪威語為''röyrkval''，意即「皺紋鯨魚」<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.iberianature.com/trivia/etymology_mammals.htm | title = Etymology of mammal names | publisher = IberiaNature - Natural history facts and trivia | accessdate = 2006-12-07 | archive-date = 2010-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100120120338/http://www.iberianature.com/trivia/etymology_mammals.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，這是因為鬚鯨嘴部內擁有一系列縱向的皺褶或溝紋，隨著身體下側延伸。鬚鯨科被認為是在[[中新世|中新世]]中期從鬚鯨演化出來的<ref name="evolution">{{cite book | url = http://www-personal.umich.edu/~gingeric/PDFfiles/PDG413_Whaleevol.pdf | format = PDF | title = McGraw-Hill Yearbook of Science & Technology | year = 2004 | publisher = The McGraw Hill Companies | chapter = Whale Evolution | author = Gingerich, P. | access-date = 2008-03-15 | archive-date = 2019-12-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191231064054/http://www-personal.umich.edu/~gingeric/PDFfiles/PDG413_Whaleevol.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 不過目前對於鬚鯨亞目中的幾個科是如何演化的所知不多。

目前確認塞鯨有兩個亞種——[[北方塞鯨|北方塞鯨]]（''Balaenoptera borealis borealis''）與[[南方塞鯨|南方塞鯨]]（''Balaenoptera borealis schleglii''）<ref name="ITIS">{{ITIS | ID = 180526 | taxon = Balaenoptera borealis | year = 2006 | date = 10 November}}</ref>。這兩種塞鯨的分布範圍各自分開，並沒有重疊。

== 描述與行為 ==

塞鯨為世界上第三大鬚鯨，僅次於[[藍鯨|藍鯨]]（可達到200公噸重）與[[長鬚鯨|長鬚鯨]]（可達到77公噸重）<ref name="mfr"/>。塞鯨的成鯨身長一般為12至15公尺<ref name="adw"/>，體重可以達到20至30頓重。南塞鯨體型比北塞鯨大，而雌鯨被認為比雄鯨來的大<ref name="nmfs"/>。目前測量到最大的塞鯨為20公尺，重量介於40至45噸之間。除了[[冰島|冰島]]之外的最大標本，長度稍微超過16公尺<ref name="martin83">{{cite journal | author = Martin, A.R. | year = 1983 | title = The sei whale off western Iceland.  I.  Size, distribution and abundance | journal = Rep. Int. Whal. Commn | volume = 33 | pages = 457–463 }}</ref>。剛出生的幼鯨一般長度為4至5公尺<ref name="adw"/>。

塞鯨的身體顏色基本上是深鐵灰色，腹部為亮灰色的，而且有一些不規則的白色斑紋。塞鯨在身體下方擁有32至60條的縐褶或溝紋延著喉部伸展，讓牠們在覓食時可以將嘴部張開到最大。塞鯨的嘴部是尖的，鰭比起其他鯨魚顯得比較短，只占身體的9%至10%，而末端是較尖<ref name="acs"/>。牠們有一道隆起從嘴部的尖端延伸到一對鼻孔，這是鬚鯨獨特的特徵。

塞鯨的皮膚常有明顯的傷疤與坑洞，這是傷口復原後的痕跡。這些疤痕被認為是由[[橈足類|橈足類]][[節肢動物|節肢動物]]<ref name="ivashin">{{cite journal | author = Ivashin, M.V. | coauthors = Yu.P. Golubovsky | year = 1978 | title = On the cause of appearance of white scars on the body of whales | journal = Rep. Int. Whal. Commn | volume = 28 | pages = 199}}</ref>、[[八目鰻|八目鰻]]<ref name="rice77">{{cite journal | author = Rice, D.W. | year = 1977 | title = Synopsis of biological data on the sei whale and Bryde's whale in the eastern North Pacific | journal = Rep. Int. Whal. Commn | volume = Spec. Iss. 1 | pages = 92–97}}</ref>或[[雪茄鮫|雪茄鮫]]（cookiecutter shark）<ref name="shevchenko">{{cite journal | author = Shevchenko, V.I. | year = 1977 | title = Application of white scars to the study of the location and migrations of sei whale populations in Area III of the Antarctic | journal = Rep. Int. Whal. Commn | volume = Spec. Iss. 1 | pages = 130–134}}</ref>所造成的。牠們擁有高且呈鐮刀狀的背鰭，高度介於25至61公分，位於背部三分之二的地方。塞鯨的照相鑑定研究的範圍通常是在尾鰭、色素模式與疤痕<ref name="schilling">{{cite journal | author = Schilling, M.R. | coauthors = I. Seipt, M.T. Weinrich, S.E. Frohock, A.E. Kuhlberg, and P.J. Clapham | year = 1992 | title = Behavior of individually identified sei whales ''Balaenoptera borealis'' during an episodic influx into the southern Gulf of Maine in 1986 | journal = Fish. Bull. | volume = 90 | pages = 749–755 | url = http://www.whalecenter.org/abstract.htm | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080305063347/http://www.whalecenter.org/abstract.htm | archivedate = 2008-03-05 }}</ref>。尾鰭則是厚與扁平的，比起身體相對較小的<ref name="acs"/>。

